WEBVTT

00:02:57.197 --> 00:03:00.987
such as liver disease 
and uncontrolled diabetes.

00:03:00.987 --> 00:03:03.849
Behaviors like smoking 
and excessive alcohol consumption

00:03:03.849 --> 00:03:07.343
also have a very recognizable odor.

00:03:07.343 --> 00:03:08.918
Regardless of cause,

00:03:08.918 --> 00:03:12.488
the bad smell almost 
always originates in the mouth

00:03:12.488 --> 00:03:15.600
and not the stomach 
or elsewhere in the body.

00:03:15.600 --> 00:03:17.430
But one of the biggest challenges lies

00:03:17.430 --> 00:03:21.765
in actually determining 
how our breath smells in the first place,

00:03:21.765 --> 00:03:23.604
and it's unclear why.

00:03:23.604 --> 00:03:25.622
It may be that 
we're too acclimatized

00:03:25.622 --> 00:03:29.193
to the smell inside 
our own mouths to judge it.

